text: Rasoul Mir Malek (born 31 October 1938) is an Iranian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Iran Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
